link:
https://github.com/MercySoh/CA3Library

This website is designed to be a library

you can login, register, view books, search books, borrow books, return them and

pay overdue fees in case you forgot to return your book

you can also update user

--Programmer defined features

-filter books by genre (Jeremiah)-
it filters the books by genre, just click on the dropdown menu and select a genre, only one genre
can be clicked at a time

found in: DisplayBookCommand, DAO in BookGenre

-password encryption (Mercy)-
encrypts the password with BCrypt

found in: UserDao

-trending books, it moves (Carlson)-
displays trending books, it is based on how many times a book is borrowed, the top 10 most borrowed ones are the trending ones

found in: dashboard.jsp, DAO in LoanDao